/* C:\Users\Edwin Boston\OneDrive\Desktop\III\STDLIB\iii\omnia\transform_patterns.iii
 *
 * III STDLIB - omnia::transform_patterns
 *
 * Register the 24 transform patterns at boot, with real fn-pointers to
 * the per-codec implementations.
 * FROZEN SPEC §7B.6, §Z.C.7; ADR-RES-006.
 *
 * Slots 18..41. Each pattern's dispatch_fn is the corresponding tp_*.iii
 * codec. The g_transform_attrs side-table records (src_form, dst_form,
 * transform_fn) for each slot.
 *
 * Hexad: kind_compose. Ring: R0. K: 0.95.
 */

module omnia_transform_patterns

